        <h4 class="font-bold text-text mb-4">바로가기</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">
          <li><a class="hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="/subscribe">무료 구독</a></li>
          <li><a class="hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="/vip">VIP 구독</a></li>
